    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Is this the right engagement?</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Consulting vs the other QuickBooks engagements.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:72ch;">Consulting is one of several QuickBooks engagement types. Where a bounded engagement fits better, the comparison below points to the right one &mdash; we hold no reseller incentive in any direction.</p>
